<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4576855>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 7. SEM micrographs of the pupa of Hydroscapha takahashii. A–C, habitus (A, ventral view; B, dorsal view; C, lateral view). D, E, details of lateral lobes of abdominal segments I–III with spiracles; F, detail of lateral portions of abdomen, ventral view; G, detail of spiracle on abdominal segment IV; H, abdominal apex, dorsal view. For high resolution micrographs see https://zenodo.org/deposit/3537900." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4576855/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4576849>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 4. External diagnostic characters of Hydroscapha takahashii (A–C), H. shuihau, new species (D–F), and H. hunanensis (G–I). A, D, G, antenna; B, E, H, male abdominal apex in ventral view with groups of setae on sternite V; C, F, I, mesoventral elevation." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4576849/files/figure.png" .

